</div><div class="news-item omega"><a href="http://www.et.byu.edu/news/supermileage-vehicle-standout" title=""><span class="img" data-alt="Looking like a jelly bean on wheels, BYU's car zips down the highway" data-src="http://home.byu.edu/home/sites/default/files/Supermileage.jpg"></span></a><h3><a href="http://www.et.byu.edu/news/supermileage-vehicle-standout" title="">BYU's supermileage vehicle a standout</a></h3><p>A team of BYU mechanical engineering students placed second and brought home the Newcomer of the Year title at their first ever SAE Supermileage Vehicle competition in Marshall, Mich. Their vehicle reached 1,135 miles per gallon. <a href="http://www.et.byu.edu/news/supermileage-vehicle-standout">Read more</a>.</p>
